  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.netbeans.jemmy.Outputable, org.netbeans.jemmy.Timeoutable

    public class NewFileWizardOperator
extends WizardOperator
    Handle NetBeans New File wizard. It is invoked either from main menu File -> New File... NewFileAction.performMenu(); or from popup menu on folder NewFileAction.performPopup();
    Usage: 
     NewFileWizardOperator op = NewFileWizardOperator.invoke();
 op.selectCategory("Java Classes");
 op.selectFileType("Java Class");

      • invoke

        public static NewFileWizardOperator invoke(Node node,
                                           String category,
                                           String filetype)
        Selects specified node and invokes new file wizard by default action. In "Choose File Type" wizard's page it selects given category and filetype. It returns instance of NewFileWizardOperator representing "Name and Location" page of the wizard.
        Parameters:
        node - node which should be selected before new file wizard is invoked
        category - category to be selected
        filetype - file type to be selected (exact name - not substring)
        Returns:
        instance of NewFileWizardOperator
